place of COVID-19 pandemic, Prime Minister Narendra Modi and Xi Jinpi...</p></div></li><li><div class="img_ctn"><a href="https://economictimes.indiatimes.com/blogs/et-commentary/emerging-opportunities-for-web-professionals-in-a-post-covid-world/" target="_blank"><img align="left" alt="Emerging opportunities for web professionals in a post Covid World" border="0" src="https://economictimes.indiatimes.com/blogs/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/Commentary-52x52.png" title="Emerging opportunities for web professionals in a post Covid World"/></a></div><div class="story_content"><h2><a href="https://economictimes.indiatimes.com/blogs/et-commentary/emerging-opportunities-for-web-professionals-in-a-post-covid-world/" target="_blank">Emerging opportunities for web professionals in a post Covid World</a></h2><p>By Manish Dalal Internet was formally introduced to India 25 years ago, on 15th August 1995. Today, two and half decades later, those ultra-...</p></div></li></ul></div></div><!--/opinions_commentary.cmspotime:283--><div class="clr"></div><div class="interview_section"><div class="ctn_header"><span class="ctn_title"><a href="/opinion/interviews/articlelist/2184566.cms" target="_blank">INTERVIEWS</a></span><div class="ctn_slider"><div class="slideleft"><a class="left" href="javascript:void(0);"></a></div><ul class="slide_btn"></ul><div class="slideright"><a class="right" href="javascript:void(0);"></a></div></div></div><div class="ctn_content"><ul><li><div class="img_ctn"><a data-conttype="100" href="/opinion/interviews/fiscal-mismanagement-is-the-root-cause-of-indias-economic-issues-says-viral-acharya/articleshow/77232452.cms"><img alt="Fiscal mismanagement is the root cause of India's economic issues, says Viral Acharya" border="0" height="141" src="https://img.etimg.com/thumb/width-188,height-125,msid-77232452/fiscal-mismanagement-is-the-root-cause-of-indias-economic-issues-says-viral-acharya.jpg" title="Fiscal mismanagement is the root cause of India's economic issues, says Viral Acharya" width="188"/></a></div><div class="story_content"><h2><a alt="Fiscal mismanagement is the root cause of India's economic issues, says Viral Acharya" data-conttype="100" href="/opinion/interviews/fiscal-mismanagement-is-the-root-cause-of-indias-economic-issues-says-viral-acharya/articleshow/77232452.cms" title="Fiscal mismanagement is the root cause of India's economic issues, says Viral Acharya">Fiscal mismanagement is the root cause of India's economic issues, says Viral Acharya</a></h2><p>As a deputy governor at the Reserve Bank of India, Viral Acharya drove banking sector reforms, brought in systems to fix regulatory leakages and block escape routes used by unscrupulous corporates. Acharya quit months before his term was due to end, fighting for the regulator’s autonomy.</p></div></li><li><div class="img_ctn"><a href="/opinion/interviews/bihar-election-calendar-to-be-worked-out-keeping-covid-concerns-in-mind-cec-arora/articleshow/77232122.cms"><img alt="Bihar election calendar to be worked out keeping Covid concerns in mind: CEC Arora" border="0" height="141" src="https://img.etimg.com/thumb/width-188,height-125,msid-77232122/bihar-election-calendar-to-be-worked-out-keeping-covid-concerns-in-mind-cec-arora.jpg" title="Bihar election calendar to be worked out keeping Covid concerns in mind: CEC Arora" width="188"/></a></div><div class="story_content"><h2><a alt="Bihar election calendar to be worked out keeping Covid concerns in mind: CEC Arora" href="/opinion/interviews/bihar-election-calendar-to-be-worked-out-keeping-covid-concerns-in-mind-cec-arora/articleshow/77232122.cms" title="Bihar election calendar to be worked out keeping Covid concerns in mind: CEC Arora">Bihar election calendar to be worked out keeping Covid concerns in mind: CEC Arora</a></h2><p>​Optional postal ballot voting facility will be provided to those above 80 years, persons with disability.  The SVEEP (systematic voter education and electoral participation) strategy is being modified to ensure that ‘no voter is left behind’. </p></div></li><li><div class="img_ctn"><a href="/opinion/interviews/a-session-can-be-called-at-a-short-notice-but-these-are-special-circumstances-due-to-covid-kalraj-mishra/articleshow/77231956.cms"><img alt="A session can be called at a short notice but these are special circumstances due to Covid: Kalraj Mishra" border="0" height="141" src="https://img.etimg.com/thumb/width-188,height-125,msid-77231956/a-session-can-be-called-at-a-short-notice-but-these-are-special-circumstances-due-to-covid-kalraj-mishra.jpg" title="A session can be called at a short notice but these are special circumstances due to Covid: Kalraj Mishra" width="188"/></a></div><div class="story_content"><h2><a alt="A session can be called at a short notice but these are special circumstances due to Covid: Kalraj Mishra" href="/opinion/interviews/a-session-can-be-called-at-a-short-notice-but-these-are-special-circumstances-due-to-covid-kalraj-mishra/articleshow/77231956.cms" title="A session can be called at a short notice but these are special circumstances due to Covid: Kalraj Mishra">A session can be called at a short notice but these are special circumstances due to Covid: Kalraj Mishra</a></h2><p>"​​It is wrong on the part of the CM to say that I am not calling the session because I am under someone’s pressure. I am not working under anyone’s influence. My only master is the Constitution of India and I am following it," says Rajasthan governor Kalraj Mishra</p></div></li><li><div class="img_ctn"><a href="/opinion/interviews/time-is-ripe-for-govt-to-bring-national-litigation-policy-to-reduce-cases-vp-singh-azb-partners/articleshow/77199967.cms"><img alt="Time is ripe for govt to bring National Litigation Policy to reduce cases: VP Singh, AZB &amp; Partners" border="0" height="141" src="https://img.etimg.com/thumb/width-188,height-125,msid-77199967/time-is-ripe-for-govt-to-bring-national-litigation-policy-to-reduce-cases-vp-singh-azb-partners.jpg" title="Time is ripe for govt to bring National Litigation Policy to reduce cases: VP Singh, AZB &amp; Partners" width="188"/></a></div><div class="story_content"><h2><a alt="Time is ripe for govt to bring National Litigation Policy to reduce cases: VP Singh, AZB &amp; Partners" href="/opinion/interviews/time-is-ripe-for-govt-to-bring-national-litigation-policy-to-reduce-cases-vp-singh-azb-partners/articleshow/77199967.cms" title="Time is ripe for govt to bring National Litigation Policy to reduce cases: VP Singh, AZB &amp; Partners">Time is ripe for govt to bring National Litigation Policy to reduce cases: VP Singh, AZB &amp; Partners</a></h2><p>"Government should consider the promulgation of a National Litigation Policy which provides for a comprehensive, consistent and considered approach to Government litigation. This would help as the Government being the biggest litigant in the Indian court system will have the ability to end the litigations on a rule-based system i.e. without allegations of fear or favour," says Vijayendra Pratap Singh.</p></div></li><li><div class="img_ctn"><a href="/news/politics and nation/need-to-remove-fear-of-covid-to-kickstart-business-chief-minister-arvind-kejriwal/articleshow/77178117.cms"><img alt="Need to remove fear of Covid to kickstart business: Chief Minister Arvind Kejriwal" border="0" height="141" src="https://img.etimg.com/thumb/width-188,height-125,msid-77178211/need-to-remove-fear-of-covid-to-kickstart-business-chief-minister-arvind-kejriwal.jpg" title="Need to remove fear of Covid to kickstart business: Chief Minister Arvind Kejriwal" width="188"/></a></div><div class="story_content"><h2><a alt="Need to remove fear of Covid to kickstart business: Chief Minister Arvind Kejriwal" href="/news/politics and nation/need-to-remove-fear-of-covid-to-kickstart-business-chief-minister-arvind-kejriwal/articleshow/77178117.cms" title="Need to remove fear of Covid to kickstart business: Chief Minister Arvind Kejriwal">Need to remove fear of Covid to kickstart business: Chief Minister Arvind Kejriwal</a></h2><p>"Home isolation was very critical... It was projected that by July 31, Delhi will have 5.5 lakh Covid-19 cases and 80,000 beds would be required...In case Delhi had reported 50,000 active cases, there would have been a severe shortage of beds, revealed Kejriwal in an exclusive interview.</p></div></li><li><div class="img_ctn"><a href="/opinion/interviews/novartis-turning-to-technology-to-manage-business-bertrand-bodson-chief-digital-officer/articleshow/77078693.cms"><img alt="Novartis turning to technology to manage business: Bertrand Bodson, Chief Digital Officer" border="0" height="141" src="https://img.etimg.com/thumb/width-188,height-125,msid-77078693/novartis-turning-to-technology-to-manage-business-bertrand-bodson-chief-digital-officer.jpg" title="Novartis turning to technology to manage business: Bertrand Bodson, Chief Digital Officer" width="188"/></a></div><div class="story_content"><h2><a alt="Novartis turning to technology to manage business: Bertrand Bodson, Chief Digital Officer" href="/opinion/interviews/novartis-turning-to-technology-to-manage-business-bertrand-bodson-chief-digital-officer/articleshow/77078693.cms" title="Novartis turning to technology to manage business: Bertrand Bodson, Chief Digital Officer">Novartis turning to technology to manage business: Bertrand Bodson, Chief Digital Officer</a></h2><p>Swiss drugmaker Novartis is turning to tech to deal with the pharma business in times of pandemic, as companies go virtual. Bertrand Bodson, chief digital officer, Novartis, in an interview shares how the company is innovating its business in the time of pandemic.</p></div></li><li><div class="story_content"><h2><a alt="Russian sovereign wealth fund in touch with India to share advanced practices on Covid vaccine: CEO" href="/news/international/world news/russian-sovereign-wealth-fund-in-touch-with-india-to-share-advanced-practices-on-covid-vaccine-ceo/articleshow/77077938.cms" title="Russian sovereign wealth fund in touch with India to share advanced practices on Covid vaccine: CEO">Russian sovereign wealth fund in touch with India to share advanced practices on Covid vaccine: CEO</a></h2><p>"RDIF is cooperating with Indian partners to share the most advanced practices to combat coronavirus, we have been in touch through the whole coronavirus period," Kirill Dmitriev said.</p></div></li><li><div class="img_ctn"><a data-conttype="100" href="/opinion/interviews/india-is-only-at-the-start-of-the-agriculture-technology-revolution-says-pablo-erat/articleshow/77068723.cms"><img alt="India is only at the start of the agriculture technology revolution, says Pablo Erat" border="0" height="141" src="https://img.etimg.com/thumb/width-188,height-125,msid-77068723/india-is-only-at-the-start-of-the-agriculture-technology-revolution-says-pablo-erat.jpg" title="India is only at the start of the agriculture technology revolution, says Pablo Erat" width="188"/></a></div><div class="story_content"><h2><a alt="India is only at the start of the agriculture technology revolution, says Pablo Erat" data-conttype="100" href="/opinion/interviews/india-is-only-at-the-start-of-the-agriculture-technology-revolution-says-pablo-erat/articleshow/77068723.cms" title="India is only at the start of the agriculture technology revolution, says Pablo Erat">India is only at the start of the agriculture technology revolution, says Pablo Erat</a></h2><p>Indo-Swiss agriculture platform Pioneering Ventures plans to integrate various parts of the agriculture value chain including harvesting, collection, processing and logistics. Agriculture and dairy focussed companies MilkLane, FarmLink, Desai Fruits and Vegetables, Citrus Processing India and Samaaru are already part of the platform. </p></div></li><li><div class="img_ctn"><a data-conttype="100" href="/opinion/interviews/a-paradigm-shift-to-clean-energy-is-must-post-pandemic-says-brics-cci-vice-chairman/articleshow/77050864.cms"><img alt="A paradigm shift to clean energy is must, post pandemic, says BRICS CCI Vice Chairman" border="0" height="141" src="https://img.etimg.com/thumb/width-188,height-125,msid-77050864/a-paradigm-shift-to-clean-energy-is-must-post-pandemic-says-brics-cci-vice-chairman.jpg" title="A paradigm shift to clean energy is must, post pandemic, says BRICS CCI Vice Chairman" width="188"/></a></div><div class="story_content"><h2><a alt="A paradigm shift to clean energy is must, post pandemic, says BRICS CCI Vice Chairman" data-conttype="100" href="/opinion/interviews/a-paradigm-shift-to-clean-energy-is-must-post-pandemic-says-brics-cci-vice-chairman/articleshow/77050864.cms" title="A paradigm shift to clean energy is must, post pandemic, says BRICS CCI Vice Chairman">A paradigm shift to clean energy is must, post pandemic, says BRICS CCI Vice Chairman</a></h2><p>The BRICS Chamber of Commerce and Industry (CCI) founded in 2012 promotes business among Brazil, Russia, India, China and South Africa (BRICS countries). In an e-mail interview Sameep Shastri, vice chairman, BRICS CCI discusses the role of the body in a post-Covid 19 world, its priorities and more. Edited excerpts follow</p></div></li><li><div class="img_ctn"><a href="/industry/banking/finance/banking/if-the-economy-opens-up-fully-chances-of-recovery-are-very-good-a-s-rajeev-ceo-bank-of-maharashtra/articleshow/77049902.cms"><img alt="If the economy opens up fully, chances of recovery are very good: A S Rajeev, CEO, Bank of Maharashtra" border="0" height="141" src="https://img.etimg.com/thumb/width-188,height-125,msid-77050455/if-the-economy-opens-up-fully-chances-of-recovery-are-very-good-a-s-rajeev-ceo-bank-of-maharashtra.jpg" title="If the economy opens up fully, chances of recovery are very good: A S Rajeev, CEO, Bank of Maharashtra" width="188"/></a></div><div class="story_content"><h2><a alt="If the economy opens up fully, chances of recovery are very good: A S Rajeev, CEO, Bank of Maharashtra" href="/industry/banking/finance/banking/if-the-economy-opens-up-fully-chances-of-recovery-are-very-good-a-s-rajeev-ceo-bank-of-maharashtra/articleshow/77049902.cms" title="If the economy opens up fully, chances of recovery are very good: A S Rajeev, CEO, Bank of Maharashtra">If the economy opens up fully, chances of recovery are very good: A S Rajeev, CEO, Bank of Maharashtra</a></h2><p>"The global economy has taken a hard hit due to Covid-19. The IMF in its recently released World Economic Outlook, June 2020 has reported that the global economy is expected to contract by 4.9% in 2020, the impact would be much larger than what we have seen during the global financial crisis of 2008."</p></div></li><li><div class="img_ctn"><a href="/opinion/interviews/from-workplace-to-yoga-classes-zoom-has-changed-the-way-people-connect-aparna-bawa-coo/articleshow/77022680.cms"><img alt="From workplace to yoga classes, Zoom has changed the way people connect: Aparna Bawa, COO" border="0" height="141" src="https://img.etimg.com/thumb/width-188,height-125,msid-77022680/from-workplace-to-yoga-classes-zoom-has-changed-the-way-people-connect-aparna-bawa-coo.jpg" title="From workplace to yoga classes, Zoom has changed the way people connect: Aparna Bawa, COO" width="188"/></a></div><div class="story_content"><h2><a alt="From workplace to yoga classes, Zoom has changed the way people connect: Aparna Bawa, COO" href="/opinion/interviews/from-workplace-to-yoga-classes-zoom-has-changed-the-way-people-connect-aparna-bawa-coo/articleshow/77022680.cms" title="From workplace to yoga classes, Zoom has changed the way people connect: Aparna Bawa, COO">From workplace to yoga classes, Zoom has changed the way people connect: Aparna Bawa, COO</a></h2><p>At the end of Dec 2019, we had 10 million daily meeting participants. By the end of April, we announced that we had reached 300 million daily meeting participants... But I am not sure that anything about this pandemic is perfectly planned.. We used it as an opportunity to see how we can scale our business, says Aparna Bawa.</p></div></li><li><div class="img_ctn"><a data-conttype="100" href="/opinion/interviews/our-scale-of-localisation-depends-on-how-we-develop-our-people-masakazu-yoshimura/articleshow/77010357.cms"><img alt="Our scale of localisation depends on how we develop our people: Masakazu Yoshimura" border="0" height="141" src="https://img.etimg.com/thumb/width-188,height-125,msid-77010357/our-scale-of-localisation-depends-on-how-we-develop-our-people-masakazu-yoshimura.jpg" title="Our scale of localisation depends on how we develop our people: Masakazu Yoshimura" width="188"/></a></div><div class="story_content"><h2><a alt="Our scale of localisation depends on how we develop our people: Masakazu Yoshimura" data-conttype="100" href="/opinion/interviews/our-scale-of-localisation-depends-on-how-we-develop-our-people-masakazu-yoshimura/articleshow/77010357.cms" title="Our scale of localisation depends on how we develop our people: Masakazu Yoshimura">Our scale of localisation depends on how we develop our people: Masakazu Yoshimura</a></h2><p>Toyota Kirloskar Motor (TKM) managing director Masakazu Yoshimura is cautiously optimistic about sales prospects this year, as enquiries have touched 90% of levels seen before the Covid-19 pandemic at its dealers. As for localization of making components, he tells ET’s KR Balasubramanyam that no country has achieved 100 % localization, not even Toyota’s Japanese plants.</p></div></li></ul></div></div><!--/opinions_interviews.cmspotime:2167--><div class="clr"></div><div class="poke_section"><div class="ctn_header"><span class="poke_icon"></span><span class="poke_text"><a href="/pokeme.cms">POKE ME</a></span><p>"Poke Me" is a Saturday edit page feature in The Economic Times. This feature appears first every Wednesday morning on <a href="https://economictimes.indiatimes.com/">www.economictimes.com.</a> Best comments from readers will be reproduced on the edit page of the 