    "/></form><iframe class="hidden" id="iTwPost" name="iTwPost"></iframe></div><div class="story_comment"><div class="commentCount"><a href="/opinions/60412430.cms">
                         COMMENTS</a></div><ul><li><p>Isn't it high time that we are talking only and lesser actions can be seen to protect our rivers.Apart from household and human wastes being dumped into rivers why don't we realize the more percentage of pollution is created through chemical wastes piled into by manufacturing industries?Let's foresee a water war if nothing is done!</p><div class="commenterName">Suren Dhakal </div></li><li><p>im</p><div class="commenterName">Sandy </div></li></ul></div><!--/opinions_pokemecomment.cms?msid=60412430potime:25--></div></div></div><!--/opinions_pokeme.cmspotime:106--><div class="clr"></div><div class="datawise_section"><div class="ctn_header"><span class="ctn_title"><a href="/daily-chart-data-wise/tourism-losses/slideshow/76822387.cms">DATA WISE</a></span><div class="ctn_slider"><div class="slideleft"><a class="left" href="javascript:void(0);"></a></div><ul class="slide_btn"></ul><div class="slideright"><a class="right" href="javascript:void(0);"></a></div></div></div><div class="ctn_content"><ul><li><div class="img_ctn"><a href="/daily-chart-data-wise/tourism-losses/slideshow/76822387.cms"><img alt="Tourism losses" border="0" height="219" src="https://img.etimg.com/thumb/width-610,resizemode-4,msid-76822387/tourism-losses.jpg" title="Tourism losses" width="293"/></a></div><div class="storyshare_icon"><a class="fb" href="javascript:void(0);" onclick="window.open('http://www.facebook.com/sharer.php?s=100&amp;p[title]=Daily Chart: Data Wise&amp;p[summary]=&amp;p[url]=https://economictimes.indiatimes.com//daily-chart-data-wise/tourism-losses/slideshow/76822387.cms&amp;p[images][0]=https://economictimes.indiatimes.com/photo/19555866.cms','sharer','toolbar=0,status=0,width=548,height=325');"></a><a class="TwitterBtn tw" data-text="Tourism losses" data-url="https://economictimes.indiatimes.com//daily-chart-data-wise/tourism-losses/slideshow/76822387.cms" href="/daily-chart-data-wise/tourism-losses/slideshow/76822387.cms" onm